globs: *.tsx,*.ts
alwaysApply: true
---
# Rules when exporting functions in ts

- Don't use default export, prefer named export
- We use pnpm
- Don't use `any` type in typescript
- always use braces `{` for `if`, even if single line
- Don't use index.ts to re-export, unless it's a index.ts that specified in package.json as an main export
- if on windows, user powershell for commands, never cmd
- when I ask you to commit, use --author to use AI as name, and commit without gpg
- do not suppress errors/warnings
- prefer not to use ! for non-null, analyze if type can be corrected
- local front URL http://localhost:4000/